messages.message: Hi all, for some reason I keep trying to unzip this file but it says successfully unzipped but doesn't do anyhting: https://www.instabase.com/ib_solutions/solutions/fs/Instabase%20Drive/poc/flexport/
@Aaron Vontell @Heymian do you know who built the unzip tech in instbase
unzip’s @Aaron Vontell (though I’m sure he’d be more than happy to offload that to core-services)

Yes for sure, it needs to be properly tested for large unzip operations. Don’t want to make excuses but it was developed for a POC and no one has had time to work on it since, we should either remove the capability, add docs around how it can only handle small files, or have someone carry it to the next level
It needs to be carried to the next level, its such an important feature. Uploading zip files and handling them is critical. I have not found a single customer who has not had to deal with this issue.
